He's Baack!  Hi, there Dr. Spatz. Like you I have been reading rather than posting.  But looky, looky.  What a change in your dialog from your first postings.  Not only is there understanding but compassion as well.  I too have changed.  This site has let me see that &quot;it ain't over til it's over&quot;.  There is still much discussion and dialog to take place.  Being able to talk about a trauma is the first step of the healing process.  I enjoy reading this site as much as a good book.  And occasionally something rings my chimes and I can relate.  It's good to be able to talk and exchange thoughts and sometimes VENT!!  So keep on trucking, Doc.
